  <title>Connectivity Plugin</title>
  <p>
    The connectivity plugin allows devices to exchange information about the
    connection strength and status of mobile networks.
  </p>

  <list>
    <title>Features</title>
    <item>
      <p>Monitor remote battery level and charging state.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Configurable notifications for low battery and full charge.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Share local battery level and charging status.</p>
    </item>
  </list>

  <div>
    <title>Requirements</title>
    <p>
      To report local battery statistics to a remote device, <app>Valent</app>
      needs a battery to be reported by UPower. Consult the documentation for
      your distribution if your battery is missing.
    </p>
  </div>

